          "datePublished": "2018-07-01T22:45:29.877Z",
          "reviewBody": "I am obsessed with this recipe!  I make a big batch of this on Sunday and pack it in individual containers to have for breakfast all week long.  It is amazing made just as listed, but I have tweaked it to suit my own needs.  I use shredded sweet potato hash browns, instead of the potato, and I omit the tomatoes and add chopped zucchini and mushrooms.  I sometimes add chopped red bell pepper as well. The spices really make this dish. Thanks so much for sharing!",
