        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "datePublished": "2006-11-03T04:40:42.897Z",
          "reviewBody": "Great recipe!  Two eggs is the way to go, no falling apart and not dry.  I used all ingredients but also used corn.  I advise that you make sure to add salt and pepper and the spices to the bean mixture before adding eggs so you can adjust as needed.",
