        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "datePublished": "2008-06-12T05:19:04.337Z",
          "reviewBody": "Fun to make! I have already made it twice in the past 3 weeks.\n\nI use eggbeaters instead of real eggs, and 1-1.5 eggs (1/4-3/8 cups) seems to form the perfect consistency. I also added cilantro and mushrooms for a nice added kick. Superb!",
