          "@type": "Review",
          "datePublished": "2017-08-08T17:41:48.227Z",
          "reviewBody": "Why oh why can't we leave 100 stars? These are amazing tacos. Make extra seasoning mix to use in other recipes. I added some of it to my guacamole. Make these for your taco Tuesday get-together. Even your most carnivore of carnivores will like them. They are a bit spicy so I suggest going easy on the chipotles and add them on the side for those who like it hot. I didn't mash the lentils and enjoyed having them to bite into. The sauce thickens enough to keep it all together. Thank you for the recipe.",
