        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "datePublished": "2018-02-25T16:03:24.02Z",
          "reviewBody": "I make these at least once every two weeks and this is a great recipe especially for people like me who are new to vegetarian meals and trying to get away from meat. I do not like spicy so I do not use any of the spicy ingredients and this still comes out delicious. It is easy to make and filling and I do not miss the ground beef I would have used in the past. I love the slightly sweet taste the tomato paste gives the dish. Great recipe!",
